description: Lists the generation requests made for a bot locale.

parameters.name: botId
parameters.description: The unique identifier of the bot whose generation requests you want to view.

parameters.name: botVersion
parameters.description: The version of the bot whose generation requests you want to view.

parameters.name: localeId
parameters.description: The locale of the bot whose generation requests you want to view.

parameters.name: sortBy
parameters.description: An object containing information about the attribute and the method by which to sort the results The attribute by which to sort the generation request information. You can sort by the following attributes. creationStartTime --- The time at which the generation request was created. lastUpdatedTime --- The time at which the generation request was last updated. The order by which to sort the generation request information.

nested_params.name: attribute
nested_params.description: The attribute by which to sort the generation request information. You can sort by the following attributes.

nested_params.name: order
nested_params.description: The order by which to sort the generation request information.

nested_items.name: botId
nested_items.description: The unique identifier of the bot for which the generation requests were made.

nested_items.name: botVersion
nested_items.description: The version of the bot for which the generation requests were made.

nested_items.name: localeId
nested_items.description: The locale of the bot for which the generation requests were made.

nested_items.name: generationSummaries
nested_items.description: A list of objects, each containing information about a generation request for the bot locale.

nested_items.name: generationId
nested_items.description: The unique identifier of the generation request.

nested_items.name: generationStatus
nested_items.description: The status of the generation request.

nested_items.name: creationDateTime
nested_items.description: The date and time at which the generation request was made.

nested_items.name: lastUpdatedDateTime
nested_items.description: The date and time at which the generation request was last updated.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: If the total number of results is greater than the number specified in the maxResults, the response returns a token in the nextToken field. Use this token when making a request to return the next batch of results.
